Package com.google.enterprise.connector.spi

Interface Summary
AuthenticationManager Authentication Manager.
AuthorizationManager Authorization Manager.
Connector The root of the SPI.
ConnectorType Configuration interface for an SPI implementation.
Property A named, typed data item.
PropertyMap A bundle of unique properties, accessible by name or iterator.
QueryTraversalManager Interface for implementing query-based traversal.
ResultSet A handle to a query result set.
Session The primary access point to information from the repository.
Value A single, typed data item.
 

Class Summary
ConfigureResponse The response for most configuration commands.
SimpleConnectorType Simple implementation of the ConnectorType interface.
SimpleProperty Simple convenience implementation of the spi.Property interface.
SimplePropertyMap Simple convenience implementation of the spi.PropertyMap interface.
SimpleResultSet Simple convenience implementation of the spi.ResultSet interface.
SimpleValue Simple convenience implementation of the spi.SimpleValue interface.
SpiConstants Non-instantiable class that holds constants used by the SPI and documents their meanings.
ValueType An enumeration of the possible value types in a repository.
 

Exception Summary
LoginException Thrown to indicate unsuccessful login.
RepositoryException Thrown for general repository errors, such as connectivity problems.
